`manifest.toml` defines package identity and dependencies. `actr.toml` defines runtime and network settings. The iOS scaffold uses `ActrNode.linked`; it does not load a `.actr` package. When remote dependencies exist, `ActrService.swift` resolves their targets from `manifest.toml`.
